<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA42">
<l>pāruṇṭāṉ pārumiḻntāṉ pāriṭantāṉ pāraḷantāṉ</l>
<l>pāriṭa muṉpaṭaittā ṉeṉparāṟ pāriṭa</l>
<l>māvāṉun tāṉāṉā lāriṭamē maṟṟoruvark</l>
<l>kāvāṉ pukāvā lavai.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“He ate the earth, he spit out the earth, he dug up the earth, he measured the earth,</l>
<l>he who before created the place that is the earth”, the say indeed. Because he also is</l>
<l>the place for the earth, who is the place?</l>
<l>Those will not enter him who is for any other.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
